{
  "stem": "18572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 503.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was just, you know-- they would just come in all the time and kill people off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My cousins were 13 and 11, boy and a girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chava and Avram.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I could never speak above a whisper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, now it's very different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for the longest time, I just couldn't speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I said, I have this vivid memory of hiding under the tablecloth, hiding in corners, crawling away somewhere, always speaking in a very low voice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even when I came to the United States, if I had to speak in the class, it was always very quiet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would find it painful to speak up or to speak in a loud voice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was first married-- and sometimes, people would call on the telephone, try to sell you something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would answer the phone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would always say, can I speak to your mother?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] They always thought I was, like, 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've gotten over that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I still don't shout.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I've learned to-- to speak in public and I've overcome that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for years, it-- it always reminded me of one of those Jerzy Kosinksi books, where he talks about-- I think it was in or was it in one of his other stories?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where the boy comes out of the war, and he's mute.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how I felt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was just-- I may not have been mute, but it took a lot to get a word out of me and for me to be comfortable, you know, with people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was always hiding and crawling away somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- my mother had heard that there were a number of people from our village in the next village over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was called Zdolbunow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
